column2: SELECT TOP #   p.ra,   p.dec,  p.dered_u,   p.dered_r,  s.z,  g.lgm_tot_p5#,  g.lgm_tot_p1#,  g.lgm_tot_p8#  FROM PhotoObj AS p   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specObjID = p.ObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra AS g ON p.ObjID = g.specObjID  WHERE   s.class=&&&  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #   AND s.zWarning = #
